title: #92Noon! Schmeelk/Florio/StPeter/Raybon/Russo
description: #92Noon goes snooping on other NFL teams with Giants.com guy John Schmeelk, then Florio makes his weekly appearance. Twins president Dave St Peter on the Twins and the upcoming home opener, Action Network's Chris Raybon analyzes March Madness, and Russo Radio is live from the X in front of tonight's Wild game!
